{"tid":1047916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★《香港貧窮情況報告》-----貧窮兒童一年增五千","createTime":"2019-03-05T09:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T18:19:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"64464cd0ee15133272aaee8b7f18647775d4b151","tid":1047916,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"根據《2017香港貧窮情況報告》，當年貧窮兒童人口上升至23.4萬人，政策介入後為17.7萬人，較2016年增加逾5,000人。另外，兒童貧窮率上升0.3個百分點，達17.5%。報告還分析，新增的貧窮兒童部分來自較大型在職住戶，且大多與長者同住，當中只有一名成員工作，其家庭負擔較為沉重。<br />\n<br />\n「我們一直認為，如果政府有心的話，應該覺得（這個數字）是恥辱。」邵家臻說。若說貧窮兒童的數字是「恥辱」，那麼政府部分所謂措施就是「笑話」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2506620/org/f77417c04fbd41d893277f0a4c7c05d5.jpg/h5tzgBISMlMARLkhJiJIRBFNWc3-jz8aQ9jP9nnYz_Y?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2506620%2Forg%2Ff77417c04fbd41d893277f0a4c7c05d5.jpg%2Fh5tzgBISMlMARLkhJiJIRBFNWc3-jz8aQ9jP9nnYz_Y%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b1ff3956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1/301911/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E5%9F%BA%E5%B1%A4%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E6%9C%AA%E8%B7%91%E5%85%88-%E8%BC%B8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B4%BE%E7%B3%96%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%95%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25A0%25B1%2F301911%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%2585%2588-%25E8%25BC%25B8-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%25B3%2596%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BD%2595%25E7%2594%25A8&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcakxT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=760e60bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1/301911/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E5%9F%BA%E5%B1%A4%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E6%9C%AA%E8%B7%91%E5%85%88-%E8%BC%B8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B4%BE%E7%B3%96%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%95